that you could view as

00:00:36.492 --> 00:00:37.936
the marginal dollars,

00:00:37.936 --> 00:00:40.408
or the incremental dollars
that you're getting

00:00:40.408 --> 00:00:42.337
per person, per hour.

00:00:42.337 --> 00:00:46.673
Per person, per hour,

00:00:46.673 --> 00:00:48.875
per hour.

